@startuml 00-contexto
title ConceptArena — Diagrama de contexto (C4 Nivel 1)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  roundCorner 20
}
skinparam actorStyle awesome

left to right direction

actor "Jugador /\nEstudiante" as Player
actor "Anfitrión de sala" as Host

rectangle "ConceptArena" as System #3B82F6/7C3AED {
  rectangle "Plataforma de trivia/estudio\ncolaborativo en tiempo real\n(salas, rondas, respuestas,\nranking, voz)" as SystemInner
}

rectangle "Servidor SMTP\n(MailHog en dev,\nSMTP real en prod)" as SMTP #EFEFEF
rectangle "GitHub\n(repositorio + Actions)" as GitHub #EFEFEF
actor "Desarrollador" as Dev

Player --> System : juega, responde,\nvota en tiempo real\n(HTTPS + WSS, navegador)
Host --> System : crea/administra salas,\nbancos de conceptos

System --> SMTP : envía código OTP\n(login sin contraseña)

Dev --> GitHub : push a main
GitHub --> System : despliega automáticamente\n(GitHub Actions -> SSH -> VM Azure)

note bottom of System
  Backend: 6 microservicios Spring Boot detrás de un
  API Gateway. Frontend (React/Vite) se despliega
  por separado y consume el gateway por HTTP/WS.
end note

@enduml
